86
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,390
That ghost

87
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:24,490
can change its appearance at will

88
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:25,870
and suck people's spirit,

89
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:27,590
killing people without a trace.

90
00:07:27,590 --> 00:07:29,350
When the Yunding Night Market opens,

91
00:07:29,350 --> 00:07:31,550
