95
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:38,409
Indeed.

96
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,909
The shop owners are all scared.

97
00:07:39,909 --> 00:07:40,370
They say

98
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,909
