102
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:48,820
an exorcist to drive away the ghost.

103
00:07:48,820 --> 00:07:50,030
Also those in the wine business

104
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:51,510
and those in the jewelry business

105
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:53,170
threaten that if within today

106
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:54,710
the ghost is not caught,

107
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:56,110
they will stop doing business in Yunding.

108
00:07:56,110 --> 00:07:57,080
