115
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:03,790
we will stop doing business in Yunding!

116
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:04,420
No, no, no.

117
00:08:04,470 --> 00:08:05,390
Well...

118
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:06,070
Sheriff Lu.

119
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,230
The magistrate orders you to,

120
00:08:07,230 --> 00:08:08,030
by the end of tonight,

121
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:09,550
solve this case at all costs.

122
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:10,160
Otherwise,

123
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,160
Yunding's prosperity will be over.

124
00:08:17,710 --> 00:08:20,260
From the mortal world to the "records of anomalies,"

125
00:08:20,260 --> 00:08:20,980
sometimes,

126
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:24,190
it's separated by thousands of mountains and rivers;

127
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:25,030
sometimes,

128
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:28,270
it's just separated by a piece of paper.

129
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,920
In this journey to the west,

130
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:32,070
we've been through many hardships.

131
00:08:32,309 --> 00:08:33,750
But we've never encountered

132
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:35,150
such a strange case.

133
00:08:36,309 --> 00:08:39,110
Although the identity of the woman in the veil has been exposed,

134
00:08:39,110 --> 00:08:40,390
there is no evidence

135
00:08:40,549 --> 00:08:42,150
to prove her as the murderer.

136
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:45,620
What we need to do now

137
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:48,710
is to bring this case back from being a "records of anomalies"

138
00:08:48,710 --> 00:08:50,500
to the mortal world.

139
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:54,230
I can only make one more

140
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:55,620
deduction without any evidence,

141
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:56,420
and that is...

142
00:08:57,070 --> 00:08:58,840
this ugly woman

143
00:08:58,870 --> 00:09:00,070
doesn't exist at all.

144
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:01,910
If that's the case,

145
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:05,230
Ms. Yin must have lied.

146
00:09:05,310 --> 00:09:06,830
So did Mudan.

147
00:09:07,430 --> 00:09:09,630
And that woman in the veil,

148
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:11,630
be it her name is Lin Bei or Chu Bin,

149
00:09:11,830 --> 00:09:14,430
not a single word of her testimony is credible.

150
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:15,590
Also,

151
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:18,710
the owner of Tianyi Fabric Shop, Shen Ping,

152
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:20,390
and the maid Chang Le,

153
00:09:21,470 --> 00:09:23,100
are also suspects.

154
00:09:25,110 --> 00:09:26,970
There are five suspects in total.

155
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:28,350
Time is tight.

156
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:29,390
Each of us

157
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:30,880
will take on one of them.

158
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:32,650
After we decide on who to take on,

159
00:09:32,650 --> 00:09:33,650
what should we do?

160
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,330
Attack their minds.

161
00:09:50,370 --> 00:09:51,800
All right, all right.

162
00:09:52,110 --> 00:09:53,840
You can leave after reading it.

163
00:09:54,190 --> 00:09:56,390
You really won't let me take your pulse?

164
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,430
I didn't say I wanted to see a doctor.

165
00:09:59,430 --> 00:10:00,400
You may go now.

166
00:10:00,470 --> 00:10:01,030
Madam.

167
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:04,870
Have you not slept for a

168
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:06,150
whole day and night?

169
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,280
In the past few years,

170
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,520
you have been continuously

171
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:11,550
taking medicine.

172
00:10:13,830 --> 00:10:14,910
No.

173
00:10:14,950 --> 00:10:15,890
Then someone must have

174
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:17,210
put it in your food.

175
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:25,280
Judging from your expression,

176
00:10:25,430 --> 00:10:26,920
you probably already know

177
00:10:26,950 --> 00:10:28,410
that you've been drugged.

178
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:31,390
This drug makes you dizzy,

179
00:10:31,740 --> 00:10:33,110
your limbs weak,

180
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:35,030
restless,

181
00:10:35,310 --> 00:10:36,710
emotionally unstable,

182
00:10:36,990 --> 00:10:38,710
your speech feeble,

183
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,430
and your legs heavy.

184
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:43,310
Once you take the medicine, you fall into a deep sleep,

185
00:10:43,310 --> 00:10:45,810
but once you wake up, you can hardly fall asleep again.

186
00:10:45,810 --> 00:10:46,580
Unless,

187
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:48,790
you take this drug again.

188
00:10:50,510 --> 00:10:51,390
How do you know?

189
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:55,470
I have cured cases of

190
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:58,140
people like you who had been poisoned with a slow poison,

191
00:10:58,140 --> 00:11:00,300
when I was in my teens.

192
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:03,510
Now I run the Yunding Clinic.

193
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:06,070
My surname is Fei, given name Qiao, and courtesy name is Yingjun.

194
00:11:06,070 --> 00:11:07,730
I'm also known as Chicken Fed.

195
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,550
I've heard of you.

196
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:11,160
I've heard of you.

197
00:11:12,990 --> 00:11:14,720
You've cured many mute slaves.

198
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:17,510
I was just thinking

199
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:19,240
of coming to see you these days.

200
00:11:20,950 --> 00:11:23,150
Greetings, Ms. Chu.

201
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,400
I am not surnamed Chu,

202
00:11:29,910 --> 00:11:30,750
but Lin.

203
00:11:33,990 --> 00:11:34,590
My family lives in

204
00:11:34,590 --> 00:11:37,110
Beimang Mountain, on the outskirts of Luoyang.

205
00:11:37,110 --> 00:11:39,370
I heard you are Detective Di's disciple.

206
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:42,720
Your master's tomb is not far from my home.

207
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:45,870
I respect Detective Di for serving the country and the people.

208
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:47,150
Every year during the Cold Food Festival,

209
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:48,750
I would visit his tomb and pay my respects.

210
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:49,480
In that case,

211
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:53,350
I shall thank Ms. Chu on behalf of my master.

212
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:55,630
It's Ms. Lin.

213
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:01,920
All right.

214
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:02,870
Ms. Lin.

215
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:05,010
You already know my background,

216
00:12:05,010 --> 00:12:05,890
but I know

217
