almost nothing about you.

218
00:12:08,190 --> 00:12:09,310
I only heard that

219
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:11,120
you are a master of many skills

220
00:12:11,140 --> 00:12:13,390
and can imitate the deceased.

221
00:12:13,910 --> 00:12:14,790
I think

222
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:17,890
if one cannot communicate with the souls of the dead,

223
00:12:17,910 --> 00:12:18,950
I'm afraid it would be

224
00:12:18,950 --> 00:12:20,950
impossible to imitate them so well.

225
00:12:21,370 --> 00:12:22,690
Ms. Lin,

226
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:25,080
since you can imitate Chu Bin,

227
00:12:25,430 --> 00:12:27,110
you must know her very well

228
00:12:27,390 --> 00:12:29,750
and know of her past,

229
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:30,270
right?

230
00:12:31,430 --> 00:12:32,430
To be honest,

231
00:12:32,710 --> 00:12:36,590
I sympathize with this lady very much.

232
00:12:36,820 --> 00:12:38,710
Especially after I saw the letter

233
00:12:38,750 --> 00:12:40,350
she wrote to Li Men.

234
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,110
Between the lines,

235
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:45,440
it was filled with blood and tears.

236
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:48,310
Ms. Lin,

237
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,520
could you tell me

238
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:52,550
Chu Bin's story?

239
00:13:06,910 --> 00:13:07,740
Shopkeeper.

240
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,120
Isn't it just copying the names of medicines?

241
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,470
I can do it.

242
00:13:15,630 --> 00:13:17,240
I have studied before.

243
00:13:18,420 --> 00:13:19,790
Why don't you just give me the money?

244
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:20,830
There's no need to hire anyone else.

245
00:13:20,830 --> 00:13:21,510
Excuse me.

246
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:25,000
Is your shop in need of someone to do some writing?

247
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:32,390
If it weren't for the decline of her family,

248
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:33,460
Chu Bin would not have

249
00:13:33,460 --> 00:13:35,060
gone out to write for others.

250
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:37,590
The first time she did it was at that drug shop.

251
00:13:37,590 --> 00:13:39,790
The drug shop's business was very poor.

252
00:13:40,470 --> 00:13:41,670
But ever since Chu Bin

253
00:13:41,950 --> 00:13:43,480
helped copy the drug names,

254
00:13:43,830 --> 00:13:45,430
business started to pick up.

255
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:47,310
Many scholars and literati

256
00:13:47,310 --> 00:13:48,770
went there to get medicine

257
00:13:48,790 --> 00:13:50,790
just to see the elegant handwriting

258
00:13:50,830 --> 00:13:52,230
on the medicine cabinet.

259
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,390
Chu Bin also became famous because of this

260
00:13:54,390 --> 00:13:55,650
and wrote everywhere.

261
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:56,690
As for Li Yun,

262
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:59,430
he no longer worked as an apprentice at the drug shop

263
00:13:59,430 --> 00:14:00,830
and ground ink for her instead.

264
00:14:00,830 --> 00:14:03,100
I've seen Chu Bin's handwriting.

265
00:14:03,860 --> 00:14:05,830
It has both the vigor of a nobel,

266
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:08,710
and carries an innate gentle elegance.

267
00:14:09,230 --> 00:14:11,070
It's truly remarkable.

268
00:14:12,420 --> 00:14:14,080
Li Yun was good with his hands.

269
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:18,260
In the winter, he personally made a cotton coat for Chu Bin.

270
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:20,570
He even embroidered a plum blossom on it.

271
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,140
Chu Bin has a weak body,

272
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:26,500
so Li Yun would stew soup for her to drink.

273
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:30,190
After all, he had been an apprentice at the drug shop.

274
00:14:30,190 --> 00:14:31,910
He stewed the soup with medicinal ingredients

275
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,310
which was both delicious

276
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:34,320
and nourishing.

277
00:14:40,710 --> 00:14:41,350
Later on,

278
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:45,230
the two of them secretly pledged to spend their lives together

279
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:47,890
and decided to return to Yunding to get married.

280
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:49,630
However, there weren't a lot of

281
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:50,940
writing jobs in Yunding.

282
00:14:50,940 --> 00:14:52,940
So Chu Bin could only persuade Li Yun

283
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:55,360
to go out and find some way to make a living.

284
00:14:55,630 --> 00:14:57,830
Their classmate Fang Jiong introduced

