864
00:41:39,030 --> 00:41:40,490
you usually talk the most.

865
00:41:40,790 --> 00:41:41,990
About today's matter,

866
00:41:41,990 --> 00:41:44,190
which one of you two is going to speak up?

867
00:41:51,150 --> 00:41:51,870
I'll speak!

868
00:41:54,510 --> 00:41:56,440
Although Changle didn't admit it,

869
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:57,510
I suspect

870
